Package: threatenedperu
Type: Package
Title: A Database of Threatened Plant Species of Peru
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: 
    c(person(given = "Paul E.",
           family = "Santos Andrade",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "paulefrens@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-6635-0375"))) 
Maintainer: Paul E. Santos Andrade <paulefrens@gmail.com>
Description: This package provides convenient access to a comprehensive database 
    of threatened plant species found in Peru, based on IUCN threat categories. 
    The package allows users to verify if plant species are included in the 
    threatened species list and provides detailed taxonomic matching capabilities 
    using both exact and fuzzy matching algorithms.
